00:02:39,500 --> 00:02:57,500
this this has no cognitive capacities is just just some physics and chemistry. And yet, slowly, so over a matter of some months and maybe years, this process gives rise to these amazing morphologies and in fact, to high level human cognition that has second order, you know, metacognition and self awareness and so on.

13
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:09,500
