55
00:10:59,500 --> 00:11:14,500
And that multi-scale architecture, which is kind of unique, it's something that in engineering we're still really not able to recapitulate, although we're getting there, shows competency in many, many different spaces.

56
00:11:14,500 --> 00:11:23,500
Now, the one thing I'd like to do fundamentally is to generalize this idea of being able to perform intelligently in some space.

57
00:11:23,500 --> 00:11:32,500
So typically, we think about three-dimensional spaces. So behavior, moving the body in three-dimensional space.

58
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:39,500
